Privacy Policy
UserGuiding is an intuitive and customizable onboarding software where companies can design continuous-seamless onboarding processes, provide real-time & interactive customer support, and discover what users think about their product.
To provide our services, we collect personal data from our users. We value your data and we are committed to being transparent about the data we collect from you.
This Privacy Policy applies to
YNOT PARTNERS, INC.
(owned solely by YNOT Partners Yazilim Pazarlama Danismanlik Anonim Sirketi, located in Istanbul - Turkiye), which provides a SaaS solution to present new and existing users with a smooth experience on your websites (hereinafter ‘’
UserGuiding
’’). The terms ‘’we’’, or ‘’our’’ used in this Policy mean our organization as the context requires.
Userguiding respects the privacy of individuals, and is committed to protecting the information of visitors to the website ("
Visitors
") where Userguiding acts as the data controller, and representatives or end users of the entities that register to use the Userguiding products and services through the Website ("
Subscriber
") where we act as a data processor.
Your data privacy questions and requests should be submitted to the Subscriber in its capacity as your Controller while you are interacting with the product or services of the Subscriber.
To ensure transparency this privacy policy ("
Privacy Policy
") governs how we process personal data we collect or receive from or about you including, but not limited to the following use cases:
When you visit our Website
When you create an account and when you log in to our  product
When you download and create guides by embedding Javascript snippets and set up our Chrome Extension
When you interact with onboarding material and provide us with feedback
When we acquire your data from third-party sources
When we use the personal data of our subscribers (e.g. contact details, payment information)
Providing Customer Support
When you interact with us on our social media profiles and our blog (e.g., Facebook, Reddit, Twitter, LinkedIn)
