Internal Logs
We may also use some other information like session and usage information for fraud prevention and security purposes.
The information inside the log files includes IP addresses, browser type, Internet Service Provider, date/time stamp, referring/exit pages, clicked pages and any other information your browser may send to us. We use such information for security purposes and to analyze trends, administer the Website, track users’ movement around the Website, and gather demographic information.
